# =============================================================================
# Root .gitignore for Warcrap monorepo
# Covers .NET projects (AgentSDK, AgentTestHarness, Opponents, Tests, etc.)
# Unity-specific ignores are in UnityRTS/RTS/.gitignore
# =============================================================================

# --- IDE / Editor ---
**/.claude/
# Per-project AI instructions live in the private Claude repo
# (C:\Git\Claude\Projects\Warcrap\CLAUDE.md), loaded via a global router.
# Keep them out of this repo entirely.
CLAUDE.md
**/CLAUDE.md
CLAUDE.local.md
**/.vscode/
**/.vs/
.consulo/
*.suo
*.tmp
*.user
*.userprefs
*.DotSettings.user

# --- .NET build artifacts ---
**/bin/
**/obj/

# --- Test results / coverage ---
**/TestResults/
**/coverage.cobertura.xml

# --- Runtime output (logs, parity exports, command logs) ---
UnityRTS/EnemyAgents/CommandLogs/
UnityRTS/RTS/ParityCommands_*.csv
UnityRTS/RTS/ParityState_*.csv
UnityRTS/RTS/ParityCommands_*.csv.old
UnityRTS/RTS/ParityState_*.csv.old
UnityRTS/RTS/CommandLogs/

# --- Committed agent debug symbols (agents ship DLL-only) ---
UnityRTS/EnemyAgents/*.pdb

# --- OS files ---
desktop.ini
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store

# --- Misc legacy ---
UnityRTS/AgentSDK/nul
